              "\n",
              "      <script>\n",
              "        const buttonEl =\n",
              "          document.querySelector('#df-ba8d99f0-48c7-4e19-a31d-5c0d037c5bc4 button.colab-df-convert');\n",
              "        buttonEl.style.display =\n",
              "          google.colab.kernel.accessAllowed ? 'block' : 'none';\n",
              "\n",
              "        async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "          const element = document.querySelector('#df-ba8d99f0-48c7-4e19-a31d-5c0d037c5bc4');\n",
              "          const dataTable =\n",
              "            await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                     [key], {});\n",
              "          if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "          const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "            '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "            + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "          element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "          dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "          await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "          const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "          docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "          element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "        }\n",
              "      </script>\n",
              "    </div>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "  "

              "      padding: 0 0 0 0;\n",
              "      width: 32px;\n",
              "    }\n",
              "\n",
              "    .colab-df-convert:hover {\n",
              "      background-color: #E2EBFA;\n",
              "      box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.3), 0px 1px 3px 1px rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.15);\n",
              "      fill: #174EA6;\n",
              "    }\n",
              "\n",
              "    [theme=dark] .colab-df-convert {\n",
              "      background-color: #3B4455;\n",
              "      fill: #D2E3FC;\n",
              "    }\n",
              "\n",
              "    [theme=dark] .colab-df-convert:hover {\n",
              "      background-color: #434B5C;\n",
              "      box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n",
              "      filter: drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));\n",
              "      fill: #FFFFFF;\n",
              "    }\n",
              "  </style>\n",
              "\n",
              "      <script>\n",
              "        const buttonEl =\n",
              "          document.querySelector('#df-a502f2d9-9654-4dc2-98ac-a2dfade3a462 button.colab-df-convert');\n",
              "        buttonEl.style.display =\n",
              "          google.colab.kernel.accessAllowed ? 'block' : 'none';\n",
              "\n",
              "        async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "          const element = document.querySelector('#df-a502f2d9-9654-4dc2-98ac-a2dfade3a462');\n",
              "          const dataTable =\n",
              "            await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                     [key], {});\n",
              "          if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "          const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "            '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "            + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "          element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "          dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "          await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "          const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "          docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "          element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "        }\n",
              "      </script>\n",
              "    </div>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "  "
            ]

      "source": [
        "> **7. Check for categorical columns and perform encoding**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "-tCJMAQ_3rOx"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df.columns"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "qZAnO4C63_Ao",
        "outputId": "de5c0c96-9a82-4748-cd43-9ce9eacd4284"
      },
      "execution_count": 382,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "Index(['CreditScore', 'Geography', 'Gender', 'Age', 'Tenure', 'Balance',\n",
              "       'NumOfProducts', 'HasCrCard', 'IsActiveMember', 'EstimatedSalary',\n",
              "       'Exited'],\n",
              "      dtype='object')"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 382
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#Label Encoding\n",
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder\n",
        "from collections import Counter as count\n",
        "le=LabelEncoder()\n",
        "print('Before label Encoding: ',count(df['Geography']))\n",
        "df['Geography']=le.fit_transform(df[\"Geography\"])\n",
        "print('After label Encoding: ',count(df[\"Geography\"]))"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "GopfEen64bDY",
        "outputId": "76ed9c6a-ce4a-4b94-c5fb-a33ed84c0291"
      },
      "execution_count": 383,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Before label Encoding:  Counter({'France': 5014, 'Germany': 2509, 'Spain': 2477})\n",
            "After label Encoding:  Counter({0: 5014, 1: 2509, 2: 2477})\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "print('Before Replace: ',count(df[\"Exited\"]))\n",
        "df['Exited']=df['Exited'].replace([0,1],['No','Yes'])\n",
        "print('After Replace: ',count(df['Exited']))"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "-B5OE76I5jGw",
        "outputId": "21f17b17-55e3-400a-80ee-f8659d7a44fb"
      },
      "execution_count": 384,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Before Replace:  Counter({0: 7963, 1: 2037})\n",
            "After Replace:  Counter({'No': 7963, 'Yes': 2037})\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {

              "        async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "          const element = document.querySelector('#df-052c5b4b-eeb9-46b2-8792-7a47815c427e');\n",
              "          const dataTable =\n",
              "            await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                     [key], {});\n",
              "          if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "          const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "            '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "            + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "          element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "          dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "          await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "          const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "          docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "          element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "        }\n",
              "      </script>\n",
              "    </div>\n",
              "  </div>\n",

              "      <script>\n",
              "        const buttonEl =\n",
              "          document.querySelector('#df-e4708dde-e54e-4ff7-8786-18b39909519e button.colab-df-convert');\n",
              "        buttonEl.style.display =\n",
              "          google.colab.kernel.accessAllowed ? 'block' : 'none';\n",
              "\n",
              "        async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "          const element = document.querySelector('#df-e4708dde-e54e-4ff7-8786-18b39909519e');\n",
              "          const dataTable =\n",
              "            await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                     [key], {});\n",
              "          if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "          const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "            '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "            + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "          element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "          dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "          await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "          const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "          docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "          element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "        }\n",
              "      </script>\n",
              "    </div>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "  "
            ]
